page.title: 09A School Boys Life
page.content: I got up at 7.30 and went in to my mums bed and I went back to bed for 5 minutes.Then I went down stairs and my sister got some football stickers, she gave them to me so I stuck them on a book for 5 minutes.Next I went up stairs and had a wash,after that I went down stairs again and played with my cars for 10 minutes.Then my sister told me to get mum and dad by shouting so I did.At 7.50 my sister went to school and I said goodbye then I had corn flakes and milk for breakfast.Next I went up stairs and got dressed then I read the Daily Mirror.I got on my B.M.X boots and after that Leigh and Sue came round and took me to school.
